  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To study the effectiveness of d-ribose in treating Alzheimer's and Dementia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Clinical experience and the pathophysiology of Alzheimer's, including neuronal insulin
      resistance, suggests that ribose improves clinical outcomes. This study will add ribose 5 gm
      3 X day for 8 weeks to monitor outcomes in a pilot study.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
